MENSURATION FORMULAE (2D shapes)
SQUARE:
s = length of a side
Perimeter = 4s
Area = s2
RECTANGLE:
l = length
w = width or breadth
Perimeter = 2(l + w)
Area = l w
TRIANGLE:
b = base, h = height
Perimeter = a + b + c

RING or ANNULUS:

R = outer radius
